       &lt;p&gt;Freestyle!&lt;/p&gt;
   {% endif %}
 {% endfor %}
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Â§Â èµ‹å€¼å¸ƒå°”å€¼
å¦ä¸€ç§å¸¸è§ç”¨æ³•æ˜¯æŠŠ<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">true / false</code>å€¼èµ‹ç»™å˜é‡:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  {% assign freestyle = false %}      

